## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **tominersen GENERATION-HD1 FAIL 2021** = HTT-lowering ASO Phase 3 failure (NfL 증가 — neurotoxicity signal). non-allele-selective HTT 감소 가설 의 임상 첫 실패. quantum-VQE 의 SNP-allele-selective discrimination 이 직접 fit.
2. **AMT-130 (uniQure) Phase 1/2 2024 expansion** = first AAV-mediated HTT-lowering CNS gene therapy. AAV5-miRNA intrastriatal one-time delivery. quantum-VQE 의 AAV capsid + miRNA 결합 modeling.
3. **WVE-003/004 (Wave Life Sciences) allele-selective ASO** = SNP-targeting Phase 1/2. mutant-only HTT lowering 가 wild-type spare. tominersen FAIL 후 next-gen approach.
4. **valbenazine (Ingrezza) 2023 HD chorea expansion** = first FDA TD 2017 → 2023 HD chorea label expansion. VMAT2 selective inhibitor. tetrabenazine 2008 era 종료.
5. **deutetrabenazine (Austedo) 2017** = second VMAT2 deuterated (longer half-life + reduced BID dosing). compliance 향상.
6. **pridopidine PROOF-HD Phase 3 FAIL 2023** = dopamine stabilizer (D2 + sigma1). primary endpoint failed. sigma1 receptor neuroprotection 가설 임상 한정.
7. **tetrabenazine (Xenazine) 2008** = first FDA HD chorea VMAT2 — 만성 1L. orphan disease 첫 disease-symptomatic approval.
8. **HD K-HD + 식약처 framework + 산정특례 + 한국 HD 등록 적은 수** = K-rare-disease framework + carrier testing + 가족성 1차예방. 한국 환자 인구 작아 임상시험 한정.
9. **base editing + prime editing CAG repeat research** = first preclinical CRISPR-based HTT 분자 손상 회복. quantum-VQE 의 sgRNA + Cas9/Cas12 + base editor pocket modeling.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, HD 임상 의미 한정.

